fields.name: account_create
fields.description: Email sent to new user on account creation
fields.body_source:
Dear {{ first_name }},

Your account registration is confirmed with the user name {{ user_name }}. Follow the link below to access LSDB.

Click here to log in. LSDB is supported on Google Chrome, Microsoft Edge, and Mozilla Firefox. Other browsers may not work as expected.

Best regards,

LSDB Dev Team

Questions? Reply to this email for support.

fields.name: assigned_owner
fields.description: Email sent to new owner of a ticket/flag/task
fields.body_source:
Dear {{ first_name }},

You have been assigned as owner to a ticket in LSDB. Click here to view the ticket.

{% if ticket_subject %}

Ticket subject: {{ ticket_subject }}

{% endif %} {% if ticket_body %}

Ticket Body: {{ ticket_body }}

{% endif %} {% if ticket_activity %}

Ticket Activity:

    {% for activity in ticket_activity %}
  • {{ activity }}
    • {% endfor %}

{% endif %}
Best regards,

The LSDB Dev Team

Questions? Reply to this email for support.
fields.subject_source: You have been assigned a ticket in LSDB

fields.name: requested_file
fields.description: Notification of a long running process completion
fields.body_source:
Dear {{ first_name }},

The file you requested is available at the following link: Click here to download the file.

This file took {{ file_duration }} for the system to generate.


Best regards,

The LSDB Dev Team

Questions? Reply to this email for support.
fields.subject_source: The file you requested is available

fields.name: reset_password
fields.description: Email with magic link to change password
fields.body_source:
Dear {{ first_name }},

We recently received a request to update your password in LSDB. Click here to log in and reset your password.

If you’re receiving this email by mistake, simply ignore it.


Best regards,

The LSDB Dev Team

Questions? Reply to this email for support.
